description:
If the value natural gas is $7.00 or greater at market close according to the resolution source on the resolution date, April 29, 2022, this market will resolve to “Yes”. If the value of natural gas is less than $7.00 as of market close according to the resolution source on the resolution date, this market will resolve to “No”.

The resolution source for this market will be Yahoo Finance’s reporting of the values offered by the New York Mercantile Exchange (NYMEX), found at (https://finance.yahoo.com/quote/NG%3DF/history). Resolution will be based on the value listed in the column labelled “Close*” under the resolution date. If the resolution source is deemed unreliable, other credible media sources may be used.
